---
title: Charred Shrimp Skewers with Mexican Oregano, Pineapple-Avocado Salsa & Cilantro Rice
description: More citrusy and bright than Mediterranean oregano, Mexican oregano pairs perfectly with lime zest on these juicy shrimp skewers. The combination of tangy pineapple, creamy avocado, and spicy jalapeño makes for an unbeatable guacamole-salsa hybrid.
